#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn18.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn18.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 18 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 18 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn18.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Khandhasutta "
msgstr "10. The Aggregates "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rāhula, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Rāhula? "

msgctxt "sn18.10:1.3"
msgid "rūpaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "Is form permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.4"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante” … "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.5"
msgid "“vedanā … pe … "
msgstr "“… feeling … "

msgctxt "sn18.10:1.6"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn18.10:1.7"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn18.10:1.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "Is consciousness permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.9"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante” … "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.10"
msgid "“evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati … pe … vedanāyapi nibbindati … saññāyapi nibbindati … saṅkhāresupi nibbindati … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati; "
msgstr "“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn18.10:1.11"
msgid "nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.12"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.13"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn18.10:1.14"
msgid "Paṭhamo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn18.10:2.1"
msgid "Cakkhu rūpañca viññāṇaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn18.10:2.2"
msgid "samphasso vedanāya ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn18.10:2.3"
msgid "Saññā sañcetanā taṇhā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn18.10:2.4"
msgid "dhātu khandhena te dasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
